COMMITTEE AMENDMENT “ ” to H.P. 542, L.D. 856
1 9. Fiduciary income tax. This section may not be construed to eliminate the
2 imposition of income tax on a fiduciary.
3 Sec. 10. 36 MRSA §5200, sub-§10 is enacted to read:
